@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000

### Hello world
GET {{baseUrl}}/

### Get all events
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/events

### Filter by query string
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/events?city=Munich&search=tech

### Get one event by id
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/events/1

### Create a new event
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/events
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "API Design Bootcamp",
  "date": "2026-07-03",
  "city": "Salzburg",
  "description": "A focused workshop on building HTTP APIs with .NET."
}

### Update an existing event
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/events/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "TechConf 2026 - Updated",
  "date": "2026-09-16",
  "city": "Munich",
  "description": "Updated after the first round of speaker confirmations."
}

### Delete an event
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/events/3

### Get a missing event
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/events/999
